Package: zarafa-webapp-extbox
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp image preview plugin
 Makes it possible to preview mail image attachments,
 this will open the image in a lightbox.

Package: zarafa-webapp-feedback
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp Feedback plugin
 Feedback collector plugin for zarafa-webapp. Adds a
 'got feedback' button to the main menubar so all users
 can directly give feedback to Zarafa.

Package: zarafa-webapp-files
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp files plugin
 File manamgent integration plugin for the WebApp, allows a user
 to browse, save and attach files from a file share backend.
 Supported backends are FTP and WebDav (Owncloud supported)

Package: zarafa-webapp-folderwidgets
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp folder widgets plugin
 Folder widgets plugin for zarafa-webapp. This is a collection
 of widgets which can show the contents of some of the default
 folders for a user.

Package: zarafa-webapp-gmaps
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp google maps plugin
 Google Maps plugin for zarafa-webapp, adds a new 'maps' tab
 in the contact details which displays the location of the contact
 by using Google Maps.

