Package: zarafa-webapp-quickitems
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp quick items plugin
 Quick Items plugin for zarafa-webapp. Adds special widgets to
