Package: zarafa-webapp-statslogging
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp statistics plugin
 User interface statistics logging plugin for zarafa-webapp.
 Logs user interface usage to an unique file per user session
 in the file specified in the plugin's configuration file.

