Package: zarafa-webapp-webodf
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp WebODC plugin
 WebODF plugin for zarafa-webapp, makes it possible to preview
 ODF files by right-clicking on an ODF mail attachment.

Package: zarafa-webapp-xmpp
