  libjs-jac
Description: Zarafa WebApp XMPP plugin
 XMPP plugin for zarafa-webapp, implements a simple XMPP based chat
 client in the WebApp in the form of a widget.

Package: zarafa-webapp-zdeveloper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp developer plugin
 Developer plugin for zarafa-webapp, exposes insertion points visually
 in the zarafa-webapp. Plugin is useful for plugin developers.

Package: zarafa-webapp-zperformance
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zarafa-webapp (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Zarafa WebApp performance monitoring plugin
 Performance monitoring plugin for zarafa-webapp. Development tool
 to measure the loading performance of several WebApp stores.
